00:52:48.690 --> 00:52:52.210
And I'll go quickly
through the other series.

00:52:52.210 --> 00:52:57.020
This I like very much because it
shows the church, the chapels,

00:52:57.020 --> 00:53:02.860
St. Paul's Chapel that is
from the 1750's, more or less.

00:53:02.860 --> 00:53:07.040
And it's kind of there, and
it stays put, and everything

00:53:07.040 --> 00:53:08.740
around it kind of disappears.

00:53:08.740 --> 00:53:15.110
You know, here is the Trade
Center goes, and new, you know,

00:53:15.110 --> 00:53:17.440
some new building goes there.

00:53:17.440 --> 00:53:24.740
And then the new One World Trade
Center is starting to go up.

00:53:24.740 --> 00:53:26.550
And there it's completed.

00:53:26.550 --> 00:53:29.230
